# --- Cloud sync (optional) -------------------------------------------------
# Folio runs fully offline using your browser's local storage by default.
# To enable cross-device sync, create a free Supabase project
# (https://supabase.com) and paste its values below, then rename this file
# to ".env.local" and restart `npm run dev`.
#
# Found under: Supabase dashboard -> Project Settings -> API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
